Detailed Description

This is used as an interchange format.

A probelist made from stl containers. /// This is like ProbeListPacked, but it can be resized and modified. /// See the SpfFile readers for example useage.

Todo:

Rename this to ProbeListMutable or something better.

Put the probes in the blocks or make a bare block object for export.
